is badly damaged. The animal
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[163,778,197,250]" pageId="14">is small and immature, with the dorsal and ventral coat missing in several places.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[163,400,290,312]" box="[163,400,290,312]" pageId="14">
